title USSD Check-in — One Screen Flow

Visitor->Aggregator:Dials shortcode
Aggregator->System:Session start (MSISDN included)
System-->Aggregator:Screen 1 — "Enter tenant code:"
Aggregator-->Visitor:Display screen 1
Visitor->Aggregator:Types code e.g. 111
Aggregator->System:Screen 1 response

System->DB:Lookup tenant by code (routing_codes WHERE status=active)

alt code not found
  DB-->System:No match
  System-->Aggregator:End session — "Code not recognised, please try again"
  Aggregator-->Visitor:Error message
else code found
  DB-->System:Tenant found
  System->DB:Write visit (MSISDN, tenant_id, routing_code_id, timestamp)
  DB-->System:Ack
  System-->Aggregator:End session — "Checked in at [Tenant Name]. Show this to the guard."
  Aggregator-->Visitor:Confirmation screen
end